<plot>Aduri Aman, a young successful woman, finds herself the target of federal agents. Oddly enough, she is employed by the FBI as an analyst. Unaware of the secrets she holds, she finds refuge in a stranger, Saif. But he seems a bit too eager to help. As they race through the suburbs of Washington D.C., Aduri's past catches up to her. In this thrilling story of hidden agendas and betrayal, who can she trust and who will help her? Can she face her past? Most of all, will she unravel the secrets she's in possession of?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?024035</url></doc>
